/********GLCM201*-*GL*Account*Codes*Extract***************************/             /*LUC109*/
/*       XXC000201 - Midas HOR GL Account Codes Extract              */             /*LUC109*/
/*                 SDACODPD to FEMID                                 */
/*                                                                   */
/*       Last Amend No. LUC109           Date 14Sep16                */
/*       Prev Amend No.         *CREATE  Date ddmmmyy                */
